ncode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/recursion-control.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Recursion Control вҖ” Reason About the Problem, Audit Once, Don't Narrate the Self\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” should I reconsider whether I reconsidered\\\") is the smell; name it in вүӨ3 words and return to the problem. | Prioritize when: what it found.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18040,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/post-implementation-deep-review.md\",\n          \"title\": \"POST-IMPLEMENTATION DEEP-REVIEW вҖ” Mandatory after substantive ship\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: asserting new invariant | | Prioritize when: asserting new invariant |\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18039,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/fable-governor.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Fable-5 Governor вҖ” Reason Outward, Act, Commit, Qualify Minimally\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” do not audit the audit. | Prioritize when: the caveat changes what the reader should do вҖ” once, in the fewest words.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18038,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/deep-skill-workflow-required.md\",\n          \"title\": \"DEEP SKILLS вҖ” Use the Workflow, Never Hand-Roll\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” Never Hand-Roll\\\" | Prioritize when: Never Hand-Roll\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16266,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” never a grep narrowed to your own files вҖ” and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {вҖҰ} вҶ’ now M: {вҖҰ}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No rвҖҰ\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16265,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch вҖ” Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsiвҖҰ | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn вҖ” NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use expвҖҰ\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16264,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-tool-routing.md\",\n          \"title\": \"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16263,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/finding-is-a-hypothesis.md\",\n          \"title\": \"A Finding Is a Hypothesis Until You Open the Cited Code\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” never ground truth. | Prioritize when: only verdict discipline still holds: never soften an active blocker without new evidence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15815,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” never a grep narrowed to your own files вҖ” and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {вҖҰ} вҶ’ now M: {вҖҰ}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No rвҖҰ\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15814,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch вҖ” Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies вҖ” Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsiвҖҰ | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn вҖ” NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use expвҖҰ\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7589,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Architecture Audit v2 [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"005\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1498,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/024-sk-deep-research-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Specification: sk-deep-research Refinement [skilled-agent-orchestration/024-sk-deep-research-refinement/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"refinement\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8514,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/023-hybrid-rag-fusion-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Deep Research: Spec Kit Memory Feature Audit & Quality [system-spec-kit/023-hybrid-rag-fusion-refinement/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7164,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/087-speckit-deep-analysis\",\n          \"title\": \"Tasks: System-Spec-Ki [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/087-speckit-deep-analysis/tasks]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"deep\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7161,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/089-speckit-reimagined-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Research [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/089-speckit-reimagined-refinement/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"research\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-18T06:06:27.947Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 1216\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781762786725,"end":1781762787962}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0d3f2d256953d623016a338adcc3348196966ba3b54c566198"}},"id":"prt_ed9566f21001F6rqbgHsAEaVM9","sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","messageID":"msg_ed95643f00011Df2oRnwcyLEsD"}}
