{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762825894,"sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","part":{"id":"prt_ed9570179001pPM8pv5s09wn3v","messageID":"msg_ed956c11c001NNqYfrAO9q7YSt","sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","type":"text","text":"The workflow contract requires canonical artifacts (`deep-review-config.json`, state JSONL, strategy/dashboard, iterations, registry, report) and exact final verdict lines. IвҖҷll inspect the supplied scope and existing lineage directory before initializing so the run is append-safe and confined.","time":{"start":1781762818425,"end":1781762825891},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0449ea6e4223cb66016a338b0262848191a22e7aea9a84e877","phase":"commentary"}}}}
