{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1781762841113,"sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","part":{"id":"prt_ed9575a180014l5FOxQtI6ODhW","messageID":"msg_ed9575404001NhAToHILoyb4bl","sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","snapshot":"84fba014133a49a417cc27ce4934d2a18247cb32","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762853039,"sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","part":{"id":"prt_ed9577e29001SXUgAyiDhhKIFW","messageID":"msg_ed9575404001NhAToHILoyb4bl","sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","type":"text","text":"Entering `phase_main_loop` for iteration 001. The scope is broad, so IвҖҷll bias the single pass toward correctness/data-integrity risks in memory write/index lifecycle and cancellation cleanup, then synthesize with coverage gaps called out instead of overstating convergence.","time":{"start":1781762850345,"end":1781762853036},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_059242dc45a9136d016a338b224f1081919226893d879e894d","phase":"commentary"}}}}
