{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762910298,"sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","part":{"id":"prt_ed9585986001T5ZJz7YPy8qTAP","messageID":"msg_ed9584288001dAEQg1opWzVkqW","sessionID":"ses_126aa1e86ffe3voro0xMEMegIU","type":"text","text":"The mutation hook check confirms scan writes normally invalidate trigger/tool/graph caches; the cancellation paths before that hook can skip those invalidations after persisted writes. IвҖҷm checking delete semantics next to avoid mixing a separate retention concern without proof.","time":{"start":1781762906502,"end":1781762910296},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_084fda74a40cda02016a338b5a78c08191bc95113b3711e028","phase":"commentary"}}}}
