back reducer, and OpenLTM observability coverage.\n+- Maintainability review of transaction boundaries and duplicate cleanup code across delete paths.\n+- F003 is advisory unless repeated reindex load is measured as operationally significant.\n+\n+## Audit Appendix\n+\n+| Item | Result |\n+|------|--------|\n+| Artifact root binding | Bound directly to fanout override. |\n+| resolveArtifactRoot command | Not run. |\n+| Iterations | 1 of 1. |\n+| Dimension coverage | 1/4 complete. |\n+| Required protocol coverage | Incomplete. |\n+| Claim adjudication | Passed for F001 and F002. |\n+| P0 replay | Not applicable; no P0 findings. |\n+| Final iteration line | `Review verdict: CONDITIONAL`. |\n+\n+Replay result: JSONL state, iteration file, registry, dashboard, and synthesis agree on active counts P0=0, P1=2, P2=1. The terminal synthesis verdict is FAIL because `maxIterationsReached` occurred before required coverage gates were satisfied.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/logs/phase-init.log\nA .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/deep-review-config.json\nA .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/deep-review-state.jsonl\nA .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/deep-review-findings-registry.json\nA .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/deep-review-strategy.md\nA .opencode/sp