n+\n+- F001: cancelled scans can leave persisted index changes without cache invalidation.\n+- F002: stale cleanup can delete causal edges before confirming the memory delete.\n+- Coverage gate is incomplete because only one iteration was allowed.\n+\n+## Next Focus\n+\n+If continued, run security/concurrency coverage over path handling, retention, provenance, idempotency, and job cancellation surfaces.\n","additions":48,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/prompts/iteration-001.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/prompts/iteration-001.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/prompts/iteration-001.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/prompts/iteration-001.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-6/prompts/iteration-001.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,15 @@\n+STATE SUMMARY (auto-generated, review mode):\n+Iteration: 1 of 1 | Mode: review\n+Target: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remed